T02D2613:85a-1: dzny'a na satva s'a dha nam /
T02D2613:85a-3: ye shes sems dpa'i sgrub thabs //
T02D2613:85a-4: 'phags pa 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2613:85a-5: chos kun rang bzhin ye shes sems dpa' yi //
T02D2613:85a-6: ma lus bde gshegs kun gyis mtshan gyur pa //
T02D2613:85a-7: rdo rje 'chang chen kung gyi rdo rje'i glu //
T02D2613:85a-8: zab cing rgya che byang chub sems dpa' nyon //
T02D2613:85a-9: byang chub sems bskyed lhag pa'i sku ru bsgom //
T02D2613:85a-10: sgyu ma rten 'brel rnam gsum sbyor ba la //
T02D2613:85a-11: ma lus gnyis med mkha' khyab 'khor lo bsgom //
T02D2613:85a-12: ma skyes mi 'gag rnam gsum sgyu ma ni //
T02D2613:85a-13: shes rab mig gis gsal bar blta bar bya //
T02D2613:85a-14: sgyu ma brag ca nam mkha' las byung bzhin //
T02D2613:85a-15: yongs su shes nas ma zhen sems kyis bklag / rnal 'byor lam chen gsang sngags 'di yin te //
T02D2613:85a-16: ji ltar dngos rnams mkha' la gnas pa bzhin //
T02D2613:85a-17: dam tshig dkyil 'khor phyag rgya che la gnas //
T02D2613:85a-18: don ni mi shes dka' ba'i las gzhan gyis //
T02D2613:85a-19: 'khor ba'i grong gsum dag las de mi g-yo //
T02D2613:85a-20: de lta'i don shes rab bzhin nyes pa spangs //
T02D2613:85a-21: spos kyi glang pos ke te dug zos bzhin //
T02D2613:85a-22: nyes pa'i tshogs bcom gzhung tshogs yon tan ldan //
T02D2613:85a-23: 'gag pa med pa'i chos kyi rgyal por 'gyur //
T02D2613:85b-0: thugs kyi @85b gsang mdzod gtsug gi rin po che //
T02D2613:85b-1: rang bzhin 'gro kun chos rnams ma lus bcad //
T02D2613:85b-2: rgyud don dbang po rdo rje'i tshig tu gnas //
T02D2613:85b-3: mkha' 'gro'i rjes 'brangs nye bar bsdus pa yin //
